Join me in this drive review as I put the BYD Sealion 7 Electric SUV to the ultimate test! In this review, I'll share my honest thoughts on the car's performance, range, comfort, and features. From the city streets to the open highway, and off road, I'll show you what it's like to live with this electric SUV on a daily basis. Is the BYD Sealion 7 the perfect electric vehicle for long road trips? Watch to find out!

